# CRM-GIS Connector - Harita Hive Enterprise Tool
# Apache 2.0 License
#
# REST/GraphQL connector to sync GIS data with ERP/CRM systems
# Real-time bidirectional sync with Salesforce, Zoho, and more
#
# Features:
# - Real-time bidirectional synchronization
# - Support for major CRM/ERP platforms
# - Custom field mapping and transformation
# - Conflict resolution strategies
# - Audit logging and data lineage
# - Secure authentication (OAuth2, API keys)
#
# Supported Platforms:
# - Salesforce (Sales Cloud, Service Cloud)
# - Microsoft Dynamics 365
# - Zoho CRM
# - HubSpot
# - Custom REST/GraphQL APIs
#
# Data Flow:
# - GIS → CRM: Location-based lead scoring
# - CRM → GIS: Customer location mapping
# - Bidirectional: Territory management
#
# Security Features:
# - Field-level encryption
# - Role-based access control
# - Data masking for sensitive fields
# - Compliance with GDPR, SOX
#
# Usage:
# crm-gis-connector --platform salesforce --config sync_config.json
# crm-gis-connector --setup-oauth --platform dynamics365